comment:
* An attestation profile defining the security requirements for verifying the attestation of a * remote compute environment. * *

This class is immutable and thread-safe. When checking this profile against an expected * profile, it is recommended to construct the expected profile and compare them with {@code * equals()}. * * @hide * @see AttestationVerificationManager

variables.name: mAttestationProfileId
variables.comment:
* The ID of a system-defined attestation profile.
     *
     * See constants in {@link AttestationVerificationManager} prefixed with {@code PROFILE_}. If
     * this has the value of {@link AttestationVerificationManager#PROFILE_APP_DEFINED}, then the
     * packageName and profileName are non-null.

variables.name: mPackageName
variables.comment:
* The package name of a app-defined attestation profile.
     *
     * This value will be null unless the value of attestationProfileId is {@link
     * AttestationVerificationManager#PROFILE_APP_DEFINED}.

variables.name: mProfileName
variables.comment:
* The name of an app-defined attestation profile.
     *
     * This value will be null unless the value of attestationProfileId is {@link
     * AttestationVerificationManager#PROFILE_APP_DEFINED}.
